# Resolution 2004-09-07.dbg.2: New Legal Counsel

September 7th, 2004

This resolution was adopted by the Board of Directors of SPI at their
meeting of [September 7, 2004](/meetings/minutes/2004/2004-09-07).

This resolution is superseded by [2024-08-12.jln.1](../../2024/2024-08-12.jln.1).

1. WHEREAS SPI's legal counsel, Chris Rourk, has resigned,
2. and WHEREAS Cleary, Gottlieb, Steen &amp; Hamilton, represented by Greg
   Pomerantz, is willing to serve as SPI's pro bono legal counsel,

### The Board of SPI hereby resolves that

Cleary, Gottlieb, Steen &amp; Hamilton is SPI's new pro bono legal
counsel, under all the same conditions as previous counsel.

